{
  "stem": "1160.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I just know that it's-- I'm suffering.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I know that I'm suffering, and I'm desperate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I have this feeling, which is [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very scary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and those cattle trains, they really have-- you know, they have just the doors.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then when they close it, they slide it in and they close it with this hinge.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the lock, they lock it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then, they have on one end of the train, what I remember, a little square window with bars, very small.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was another one on the other side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sometimes [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] people got desperate and they were making noise, especially one of the ladies.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She started to get hysterical.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the noise was very big.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So the gun came in through this little window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And in German, it was said, if you're not going to shut up, I will shoot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And even there, I started to laugh, because this lady, who was getting hysterical because there was no place, no food, no nothing, and-- scary.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the gun was pushed through the window, so she turns to her husband in a shrieky voice-- shrieky voice she says, [INAUDIBLE], why don't you do something and tell him to-- don't point that gun?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we started to laugh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is she crazy or something?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She must have been going a little bit nuts already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember on the train-- one time I remember that after a very long time-- it must've been days-- they put in such a small breads.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was little loafs of bread, few.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are about 80 people on the train, at least.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
